ygData.messageBody:
Mistmoore is a lvl 20-50 zone, it has dark elf rogues, casters, gargolyes and
vampires. Mistmoore is some of the best exp i've gotten plus ok loot.however, on
a certain mob there is a shield called the crested mistmoore shield(rare spawn)
i dont know the stats off hand but its worth around 400p. other then that, the
rogues drop raw-hide, bronze and FS weapons, and gargoyles have eyes that sell
for 6p to vendors. fyi if your 20 a caster can drop u in 2 spells :) force shock
is nothing to mess with
